room_title: Escape room "Shock & Awe" by Countdown Games in Lexington
room_description: Nikola Tesla was an incredible inventor and mad scientist. You are applying to be his apprentice but not until you can power up his laboratory. He’s given you one hour to escape his mesmerizing lab with over 10,000 lights, lasers, giant mirror ball, plasma ball and much more in this, the world’s biggest escape game.
